    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gong chimes of Vietnam. They consist of three gongs, suspended in metal circles, which are attached to a wooden frame. Since the 18th century, they have been used in Vietnamese court music.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
